{"tid":2136797,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】麥德羅與劉少君康復嘆茶慶祝：好似生離死別咁","createTime":"2020-08-02T11:53:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-02T12:25:28.000Z","uid":351978,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"974db5d3d2d4c3450aff43570889b5816077cedd","tid":2136797,"uid":351978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:53:46.000Z","msg":"娛圈近日爆出武漢肺炎傳播鏈，麥德羅、其女友Apple姐、歌手施匡翹、宣傳人員阿佳、劉少君、新城電台高層和員工等全部確診。<br />\n<br />\n劉少君前日康復出院後，昨日輪到麥德羅出院，兩個好兄弟今日即急不及待到酒樓嘆茶見面，慶祝齊齊康復。麥德羅說：「出咗院第一次可以飲茶啦，同好兄弟劉少君兩個可以揸住杯茶飲吓茶，但限聚令都係兩個。」他又表示：「好耐冇飲過茶啦，今日同我老友記互相問好，好似生離死別咁。」劉少君就表示：「最緊要注要衞生、注意安全，病毒周圍都會有嘅，我哋只要注意衞生，一定可以將佢擊破嘅。」麥德羅提醒大家進食後即戴上口罩及勤洗手，並說：「我哋大家傾吓好返之後點補養返個肺，千祈唔好咁勞碌，同埋唔好咁劇烈嘅運動。大家小心，一齊努力抗疫。」劉少君指現時疫情仍非常嚴峻，若老人家不幸中招也不用擔心：「一定醫得到嘅，一定有希望嘅，唔好氣餒，大家都要注重衞生，呢段時間我同麥德羅會加強我哋體魄嘅，將我哋心肺恢復得比以前更加好。」<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者問劉少君其他茶客見到他與麥德羅坐在一起飲茶可會驚慌，或是二人受到歧視？劉少君說：「絕對冇驚我哋，香港人係支持香港人嘅，更加冇歧視我哋，因為大家都係香港人吖嘛，有病就醫返好，咁咪冇事囉。希望所有傳媒畀多啲正能量老人家，患咗呢個病症嘅，等佢哋有多啲勇氣接受呢個醫治。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200802/MIDOH5K47CB2YOC5MIHZ4E7OXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200802%2FMIDOH5K47CB2YOC5MIHZ4E7OXU%2F&d=aFheyUS8Hi5o9a%2F4VMBAnezsNYmc6RwURZU94nRINXI%3D&h=704903d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200802%2FMIDOH5K47CB2YOC5MIHZ4E7OXU%2F&h=f804b98e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200802/MIDOH5K47CB2YOC5MIHZ4E7OXU/</a><img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fDGFIInGKMDE7gdTs6czQ-WMEuk=/640x360/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2WKBJ2AL3MJEUPIYHGYWOU6HKM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfDGFIInGKMDE7gdTs6czQ-WMEuk%3D%2F640x360%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2WKBJ2AL3MJEUPIYHGYWOU6HKM.jpg&h=230295ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ad552047124d9ece17ea7d7c274ac29384e5d06","tid":2136797,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T11:57:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">空姐牛肉飯影相手足被控襲擊<br />\n聽朝9:30西九龍裁判法院提堂</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2136461\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2136461</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RzbrTe9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRzbrTe9.jpg&h=4dde1260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evWoa1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevWoa1T.jpg&h=1a1d615b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"teal\"><strong>可唔可以陪手足一齊早起身一次阿？</strong></span>"},{"pid":"167c00b269d529ca0f37535f4d5c3a62cd2d8fdd","tid":2136797,"uid":8014,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T12:00:03.000Z","msg":"武漢感冒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2件廢老中完一d 事都無"},{"pid":"89c540d67cce807ef1ef7dda42809ddf5c50909c","tid":2136797,"uid":351978,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T12:01:21.000Z","msg":"睇到佢哋飲茶嗰幅相，就知點解佢哋會賴嘢<br />\n真係靈頑不靈，無藥可救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85020f0c8b23413556acf4d376567a2acbd060d","tid":2136797,"uid":283071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T12:11:45.000Z","msg":"麥德羅算唔算係第一個靠武肺上位既藝人？<br />\n<br />\n利申:廿到尾 之前聽都未聽過佢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"112f5b57579ba39eb50a507436fc701fd7f3923b","tid":2136797,"uid":181819,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-02T12:19:33.000Z","msg":"成世人最出位今次"},{"pid":"3154a5cc64d66ac04013675bb1f76def06290b3c","tid":2136797,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2